What is it?
===========

xfce4 panel plugin for show namedays. 
Inspired by (GdH, J. Nekvasila) applet for Gnome2 and Unity


Installation
============
./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr/
make
make install (as root)


How to report bugs?
===================
Let's go to https://bugs.launchpad.net/xfce4-nameday-plugin and fill a Bug Report
